## Repository Structure

```
{{REPO_NAME}}/
├── Docs/                  Infrastructure documentation
│   ├── Network_Inventory.md       IP allocation, device specs, capacity
│   └── CHANGELOG.md               All significant changes
├── Planning/              Active plans and questionnaires
├── Workflows/             Automation workflow exports and configs
│   ├── Exports/           Raw workflow JSON exports
│   ├── Configs/           Connection configs (no secrets)
│   └── Reviews/           Workflow analysis notes
├── Knowledge/             Operational knowledge and notes
│   ├── Procedures/        SOPs and runbooks
│   ├── Client-Notes/      Per-client technical notes (no PII)
│   └── Vendor-Notes/      Vendor-specific reference info
├── Operations/            Day-to-day operational tracking
│   ├── Change-Log/        Infrastructure changes with dates
│   ├── Incidents/         Issue tracking and resolution
│   └── Maintenance/       Scheduled maintenance records
├── Reviews/               AI-assisted analysis outputs
├── Scripts/               Environment-specific scripts
├── Outputs/               Generated reports and deliverables
└── Archive/               Retired files (never delete — move here)
```

