## Quick Reference

### Git Workflow

```bash
# Daily start
git pull

# After any change
git add -A
git commit -m "Brief description"
git push
```

### Change Management

See [Git-Organized.md](Git-Organized.md) for the full change workflow:
Duplicate → Modify → Evaluate → Confirm → Archive → Implement → Update

